            Visibility will inform your policy customization decisions. For example, you may find that a 
            high risk application such as <i>baofeng</i> is consuming an inordinate amount of bandwidth. If so, you 
            can use the CFS Portal to edit an Application Control policy to block it, or you can enlist the 
            help of the Allstream Network Operations Center.
        </p>
