            <li class="ulli"><b>Continue: </b>Allows the user to access the blocked page by clicking the “Continue” button on the blocked page.
                    An alert is added to the URL Filtering log.</li>
            <li class="ulli"><b>Block: </b>Blocks access to the page and adds an alert to the URL Filtering log.</li>
